text: ONEOK, Inc. (pronounced like 'one oak') () is a diversified Fortune 200 corporation based in Tulsa, Oklahoma. Founded in 1906 as Oklahoma Natural Gas Company, it is one of the largest natural gas distributors in the United States. ==Other websites== * ONEOK Website Category:Tulsa, Oklahoma Category:Companies based in Oklahoma Category:1906 establishments in the United States Category:1900s establishments in Oklahoma Territory
